  <title>Tag your favorites</title>

  <p>Photos or albums can be marked as favorites from the
  <gui style="tab">Photos</gui> tab or <gui style="tab">Albums</gui> tab.</p>

  <steps>
  <title>To label favorite items:</title>
    <item>
      <p>Select the <gui>Albums</gui> tab or <gui>Photos</gui> tab depending on
      whether you want to mark an album or a photo as a favorite.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Switch on the selection mode.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select all the items you want to favorite.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>To finish, select the button with the picture of a star from the
      toolbar at the bottom.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>Your favorite items can now be found in the <gui>Favorites</gui> tab.</p>

